ean-squared error by the two proposed estimators. For fractional Brownian\nmotions, both proposed methods yield estimators of $H$ that are asymptotically\nnormal and unbiased.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Mar 2017 21:19:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-14"}
