reshold below which water maser emission\ncannot be produced. Alternatively, if the correlation still stands at low\nluminosity, the detection rates of masers would be significantly lower than the\nvalues obtained in higher-luminosity Class 0 protostars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Mar 2017 10:41:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-26"}
